<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Resume Matcher Pro!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .feature {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .countdown {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4a6cf7;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Resume Matcher Pro!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>We're thrilled to have you join Resume Matcher Pro! Your 3-day free trial has started, giving you full access to all our premium features.</p>
    
    <div class="countdown">
      Your trial ends on: {{trialEndDate}}
    </div>
    
    <h2>What's included in your subscription:</h2>
    
    <div class="feature">
      <strong>✓ Unlimited job postings</strong>
      <p>Create as many job listings as you need.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="feature">
      <strong>✓ Advanced ATS optimization</strong>
      <p>Get the edge on Applicant Tracking Systems with our smart resume builder.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="feature">
      <strong>✓ All premium templates</strong>
      <p>Access our full library of professional resume templates.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="feature">
      <strong>✓ Priority support</strong>
      <p>Get help faster with dedicated support.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Ready to get started? We've prepared some resources to help you make the most of your subscription:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">How to create the perfect resume</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Tips for beating ATS systems</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Resume templates explained</a></li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help. Just reply to this email!</p>
    
    <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard" class="button">Go to Your Dashboard</a>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Resume Matcher Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>© {{currentYear}} Resume Matcher. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings/billing">Manage Subscription</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings">Account Settings</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>